    # share the love.
    we love applying our skills and drive to pursuits outside of client work as
    well. from open source projects to conferences and events to sports and
    performances, we're all about getting out there, expanding our horizons,
    and giving back.

    ## open source.

    - [cmsimple](https://github.com/modeset/cmsimple) - a simple CMS wrapped around the [Mercury](https://github.com/jejacks0n/mercury) content editor
    - [teaspoon](https://github.com/modeset/teaspoon) - a JavaScript test runner built on top of Rails for running mocha or jasmine test suites
    - [utensils](https://github.com/modeset/utensils) - a client side component driven library
    - [docomo](https://github.com/modeset/docomo) - a documentation and style guide generation tool tuned to work with the asset pipeline
    - [fishnet](https://github.com/modeset/fishnet) - a simple grid framework of functions and mixins for both fluid and fixed layouts
    - [modeset.js](https://github.com/modeset/modeset.js) - javascript experiments and testing ground
    - [chrono](https://github.com/modeset/chrono) - simple timekeeping system - make it easy to remember how you spend your hours
    - [dotset](https://github.com/modeset/dotset) - our default configuration files for Bash and Vim. [we &hearts; the Vim]
    - [bitbot](https://github.com/modeset/bitbot) - mode set's campfire bot

